requirement: The system shall verify sensor sensitivity by executing the 'Verify Sensor Sensitivity' test procedure.

The test case shall verify the sensor resolution by having the Test Operator control the Thermal Source and Unit-Under-Test to generate Thermal Emissions, sense the emissions via the System-Under-Test, process the data into Thermal Imagery through the Signal Processor and Display, then measure the resolution and assess pass/fail.
